Detailed Description

template<class T>
class XFcLinkedList< T >

Bidirectional linked list template class.

Example: 

 // Create the list
 XFcLinkedList<UINT32> *list = new XFcLinkedList<UINT32>();
 list->addLast(1);
 list->addLast(2);
 list->addLast(3);
 list->addLast(4);
 list->removeIndex(2);
 // The list now contains items {1, 2, 4}
 delete list;
